name: Doctor Strange Collection
overview: This series tells the story of neurosurgeon Stephen Strange who, after losing the ability to use his hands after a car accident, seeks the help of The Ancient One to become a Master of the Mystic Arts known as Doctor Strange.

parts.overview: After his career is destroyed, a brilliant but arrogant surgeon gets a new lease on life when a sorcerer takes him under her wing and trains him to defend the world against evil.
parts.title: Doctor Strange

parts.original_title: Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness
parts.overview: Doctor Strange, with the help of mystical allies both old and new, traverses the mind-bending and dangerous alternate realities of the Multiverse to confront a mysterious new adversary.
parts.title: Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness
